OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming less frequent into the
OL,7,Fevening, before skies cloud over from
OL,8,Fthe west later in the night, with more
OL,9,Forganised showers reaching the region
OL,10,Ftowards dawn. Feeling cool still.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FShowery rain breaking up
OL,13,Fthrough the morning, then sunshine and
OL,14,Fa continued risk of showers with hail
OL,15,Fand thunder, before these fade towards
OL,16,Fevening. Winds lighter than Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
