OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fspell of wet and windy weather moves
OL,7,Fin for Thursday. Largely cloudy on
OL,8,FFriday with patchy rain. High pressure
OL,9,Fdeveloping from Saturday bringing
OL,10,Fsunny spells and rising temperatures.
